amstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601580/extras/yol_bul.gif?t=1734297876\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To find your way in the dark, you need to use the flash of the camera where your memories are buried to illuminate your path and continue. However, you must use the flash at the right moments because it has a limited duration, and if you can't manage the timing, bad things can happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601580/extras/Calsma_Yuzeyi_3.png?t=1734297876\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601580/extras/\u00e7e\u015fitlilik.gif?t=1734297876\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will be present in multiple locations to learn about the purpose and secrets of the Paradise Company. All these locations are independent, carefully chosen places for you to uncover the company's secrets. While uncovering these secrets, you must also experience all the pain and fear that has occurred there, but in the end, you will confront the absolute truth. Remember, you must always bear the pain of the damaged lives left unfinished.</p>","developers":["Entry Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601580/header.jpg?t=1734297876","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257078266,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078266/movi